{"title":"坚决消灭“活阎王”","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":4,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决消灭“活阎王”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大哥，请细听："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎贼是个吃人精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统治山西四十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祸国殃民坏透顶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人都骂他“活阎王”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"害人花样数不清："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“兵农合一”巧抓丁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓走弟弟又抓兄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家有土地没人种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有点粮食也“充公”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“自白转生”要人命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱棍铡刀不留情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十家就有九家空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"害得百姓活不成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们要想知民底细，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住下问问老百姓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们军队大会合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一举打下太原城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决消灭“活阎王”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖掉山西老祸根。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}